      "subject": "This week: Janet Martin, Dave Caputo & more",
      "htmlBody": "<!doctype html><html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\">\n<meta name=\"color-scheme\" content=\"light\">\n<meta name=\"supported-color-schemes\" content=\"light\">\n<meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n<title>The Quarry</title>\n\n        <style>\n            .qbody { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; color: #2c2c2c; line-height: 1.65; }\n            .qbody h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; color: #1a2942; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0 0 18px; font-weight: 700; }\n            .qbody h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; color: #1a2942; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.3; margin: 28px 0 14px; font-weight: 700; }\n            .qbody h3 { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; color: #9a7b2a; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.3; margin: 24px 0 8px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.16em; font-weight: 700; }\n            .qbody p  { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #2c2c2c; margin: 0 0 16px; }\n            .qbody ul, .qbody ol { margin: 0 0 16px 18px; padding: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; }\n            .qbody li { margin: 0 0 8px; }\n            .qbody a  { color: #9a7b2a; text-decoration: underline; }\n            .qbody hr { border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #d4ccb3; margin: 24px 0; }\n            .qbody .event-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); border-left: 4px solid #9a7b2a; padding: 14px 16px; margin: 0 0 14px; border-radius: 4px; }\n            .qbody .event-date { font-size: 12px; color: #9a7b2a; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; margin: 0 0 4px; }\n            .qbody .event-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 18px; color: #1a2942; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 4px; }\n            .qbody .event-meta { font-size: 13px; color: #6b6b6b; margin: 0; }\n        </style>\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#1a2942;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;\">\n\n<!-- Outer navy canvas -->\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background:#1a2942;\">\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:24px 12px;\">\n\n    <!-- Email card (cream parchment) -->\n    <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;background:#f5efde;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);\">\n\n      <!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550 NAVY MAST: gold Q + brand + linked tagline \u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n      <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"background:#1a2942;padding:24px 24px 18px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;\">\n          <img src=\"https://thequarrystl.com/assets/quarry-q-logo.png\" alt=\"The Quarry\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" style=\"display:block;margin:0 auto 8px;border:0;outline:none;\">\n        </a>\n        <div style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:24px;color:#f3ecd9;letter-spacing:0.14em;font-weight:700;line-height:1;\">THE QUARRY</div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;color:#c9a44a;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:10px;font-weight:600;\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/quarry-drinks.html?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=header-tagline&utm_content=drinks\" style=\"color:#c9a44a;text-decoration:none;\">Drinks</a> &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp;\n          <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/quarry-menu.html?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=header-tagline&utm_content=bites\"   style=\"color:#c9a44a;text-decoration:none;\">Bites</a> &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp;\n          <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/quarry-bands.html?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=header-tagline&utm_content=music\"  style=\"color:#c9a44a;text-decoration:none;\">Live Music</a> &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp;\n          <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/quarry-golf.html?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=header-tagline&utm_content=golf\"    style=\"color:#c9a44a;text-decoration:none;\">Golf</a>\n        </div>\n      </td></tr>\n\n      <!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550 HERO IMAGE (full-bleed) \u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n      <tr><td style=\"padding:0;line-height:0;font-size:0;\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com\" style=\"display:block;\">\n          <img src=\"https://thequarrystl.com/assets/img/quarry-hero-1280.jpg\" alt=\"The Quarry \u2014 patio, live music, and the lake at sunset\" width=\"600\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;max-width:600px;height:auto;border:0;outline:none;\">\n        </a>\n      </td></tr>\n\n      <!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550 BODY (cream, AI-generated content rendered with .qbody styles) \u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n      <tr><td class=\"qbody\" style=\"background:#f5efde;padding:32px 32px 16px;\">\n        <h3>THIS WEEK AT THE QUARRY</h3>\n\n<p>Three live acts this week, {firstName} \u2014 no cover, no reservation needed. Just walk in, find your spot, and enjoy.</p>\n\n<div class=\"event-card\">\n  <div class=\"event-date\">FRI \u00b7 APR 30</div>\n  <div class=\"event-title\">Live Music: Janet Martin</div>\n  <div class=\"event-meta\">7 PM \u2013 10 PM \u00b7 No cover \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\">Details</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"event-card\">\n  <div class=\"event-date\">SAT \u00b7 MAY 1</div>\n  <div class=\"event-title\">Live Music: Dave Caputo</div>\n  <div class=\"event-meta\">1 PM \u2013 4 PM \u00b7 No cover \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\">Details</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"event-card\">\n  <div class=\"event-date\">SUN \u00b7 MAY 2</div>\n  <div class=\"event-title\">Live Music: Mixology</div>\n  <div class=\"event-meta\">1 PM \u2013 4 PM \u00b7 No cover \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\">Details</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Walk-ins are always welcome. Live music is free with your visit \u2014 just show up, find a seat, and let the week take care of itself.</p>\n\n<p>See you soon,<br>The Quarry</p>\n      </td></tr>\n\n      <!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550 PRIMARY CTA BUTTON (gold, large, centered) \u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n      <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"background:#f5efde;padding:8px 32px 32px;\">\n        <table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n          <tr><td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#9a7b2a\" style=\"border-radius:6px;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(154,123,42,0.35);\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/quarry-private-events.html?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=footer-cta\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:16px 36px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;\">\n              Book Your Next Event &nbsp;\u2192\n            </a>\n          </td></tr>\n        </table>\n        <div style=\"font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#6b6b6b;margin-top:14px;letter-spacing:0.04em;\">\n          Wed\u2013Sun &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; New Melle, MO &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; <a href=\"tel:6362248257\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;\">(636) 224-8257</a>\n        </div>\n      </td></tr>\n\n      <!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550 NAVY FOOTER: follow us text + address + unsub \u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n      <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"background:#0f1a2e;padding:24px 24px 22px;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#f3ecd9;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;\">Follow Us</div>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.04em;\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thequarrystl\" style=\"color:#c9a44a;text-decoration:none;\">Facebook</a> &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp;\n            <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thequarrystl\" style=\"color:#c9a44a;text-decoration:none;\">Instagram</a> &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp;\n            <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com\" style=\"color:#c9a44a;text-decoration:none;\">Website</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:16px;color:#c9a44a;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.06em;margin-bottom:4px;\">The Quarry</div>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#f3ecd9;line-height:1.5;\">3960 Highway Z &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; New Melle, MO 63385 &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; <a href=\"tel:6362248257\" style=\"color:#f3ecd9;text-decoration:none;\">(636) 224-8257</a></div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:rgba(243,236,217,0.55);line-height:1.6;\">\n          You're receiving this because you signed up, booked an event, or attended one at The Quarry.<br>\n          <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/.netlify/functions/unsubscribe?email={email}\" style=\"color:rgba(243,236,217,0.75);text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a> &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp;\n          <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/privacy.html\" style=\"color:rgba(243,236,217,0.75);text-decoration:underline;\">Privacy Policy</a>\n        </div>\n      </td></tr>\n\n    </table>\n\n    <!-- Below-card: tiny brand watermark -->\n    <div style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;color:rgba(243,236,217,0.30);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;margin-top:18px;\">\u2014 THE QUARRY \u2014</div>\n\n  </td></tr>\n</table>\n</body></html>",
      "innerHtml": "<h3>THIS WEEK AT THE QUARRY</h3>\n\n<p>Three live acts this week, {firstName} \u2014 no cover, no reservation needed. Just walk in, find your spot, and enjoy.</p>\n\n<div class=\"event-card\">\n  <div class=\"event-date\">FRI \u00b7 APR 30</div>\n  <div class=\"event-title\">Live Music: Janet Martin</div>\n  <div class=\"event-meta\">7 PM \u2013 10 PM \u00b7 No cover \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\">Details</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"event-card\">\n  <div class=\"event-date\">SAT \u00b7 MAY 1</div>\n  <div class=\"event-title\">Live Music: Dave Caputo</div>\n  <div class=\"event-meta\">1 PM \u2013 4 PM \u00b7 No cover \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\">Details</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"event-card\">\n  <div class=\"event-date\">SUN \u00b7 MAY 2</div>\n  <div class=\"event-title\">Live Music: Mixology</div>\n  <div class=\"event-meta\">1 PM \u2013 4 PM \u00b7 No cover \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\">Details</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Walk-ins are always welcome. Live music is free with your visit \u2014 just show up, find a seat, and let the week take care of itself.</p>\n\n<p>See you soon,<br>The Quarry</p>",
